---
title: Argentinian Steak & Chimichurri with Roasted Veggies
description: A juicy tender steak is one thing, but the right condiment takes it to the next level of deliciousness. We've added roasted garlic to chimichurri, a bright, fresh and flavoursome South American sauce to give the classic steak and three veg a flavourful upgrade.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/argentinian-steak-chimichurri-c81698b6.jpg
